<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 12:25:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>多边带量子模的可控确定性量子隐形传态</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/controllable-deterministic-quantum-teleportation-of-multiple-sideband-qumodes</link><description>量子隐形传态作为一种重要的量子通信协议，在量子信息科学技术领域有着广泛的应用。对于应用来说，通过同时传送多个量子态来增强量子隐形传态的能力是至关重要的。在这里，我们通过实验证明了相干态多个边带量子模式的确定性量子隐形传态，这相当于在连续变量（CV）量子纠缠的帮助下同时隐形传态多个量子态。通过根据不同的可调频率微调两个经典通道的相位，我们成功地在24 MHz的带宽内同时实现了多达5个边带量子模的确定性CV量子隐形传态。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/controllable-deterministic-quantum-teleportation-of-multiple-sideband-qumodes2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 12:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/controllable-deterministic-quantum-teleportation-of-multiple-sideband-qumodes</guid></item><item><title>这种微小的有机体在类似火星的幻觉下拒绝死亡</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/this-tiny-organism-refused-to-die-under-mars-like-illusion</link><description>面包酵母（酿酒酵母）以其在烘焙、酿造和现代生物技术中的作用而闻名。然而，这种日常微生物也可能为一个更大的问题提供见解：生命如何忍受地球以外的极端条件。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/this-tiny-organism-refused-to-die-under-mars-like-illusion.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 12:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/this-tiny-organism-refused-to-die-under-mars-like-illusion</guid></item><item><title>干细胞贴片可逆转脊柱裂胎儿的脑损伤</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/stem-cell-patch-reverses-brain-damage-in-fetuses-with-spina-bifida</link><description>作为世界首次试验的一部分，由供体胎盘干细胞制成的贴片已被用于治疗子宫内患有严重脊柱裂的胎儿。这种新方法似乎至少与首选治疗方法一样有效地逆转了与先天性疾病相关的大脑并发症，但预计将使更多的儿童能够长期行走。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/stem-cell-patch-reverses-brain-damage-in-fetuses-with-spina-bifida2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 11:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/stem-cell-patch-reverses-brain-damage-in-fetuses-with-spina-bifida</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，DeepSeek 扣留了包括 Nvidia 在内的美国芯片制造商的最新人工智能模型</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/deepseek-withholds-latest-ai-model-from-us-chipmakers-including-nvidia-sources-say</link><description>旧金山/新加坡——两位知情人士称，中国人工智能实验室 DeepSeek 尚未向美国芯片制造商展示其即将推出的性能优化旗舰模型，这在重大模型更新之前打破了标准行业惯例，其低成本模型去年震惊了全球市场。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/deepseek-withholds-latest-ai-model-from-us-chipmakers-including-nvidia-sources-say.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 11:40:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/deepseek-withholds-latest-ai-model-from-us-chipmakers-including-nvidia-sources-say</guid></item><item><title>青春期睡眠和昼夜节律多基因评分的发育知情研究</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-developmentally-informed-study-of-sleep-and-circadian-polygenic-scores-in-adolescence</link><description>成人睡眠 GWAS 衍生的多基因评分显示出与青少年相应睡眠表型的相关性，表明遗传对睡眠的影响在整个发育阶段持续存在。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-developmentally-informed-study-of-sleep-and-circadian-polygenic-scores-in-adolescence2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 11:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-developmentally-informed-study-of-sleep-and-circadian-polygenic-scores-in-adolescence</guid></item><item><title>基础模型满足医学图像解释</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/foundation-models-meet-medical-image-interpretation</link><description>相比之下，医学领域传统的深度学习方法长期以来受到标注数据稀缺、跨模态语义相关性弱、泛化能力不足的制约。 FM可以通过从大规模未标记数据中提取语义表示、减少对专家注释的依赖、增强跨模态理解和可迁移性来有效缓解这些问题。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/foundation-models-meet-medical-image-interpretation2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 11:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/foundation-models-meet-medical-image-interpretation</guid></item><item><title>无创监测灵长类动物大脑中的基因表达</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/noninvasive-monitoring-of-gene-expression-in-primate-brains</link><description>基因疗法已成功用于治疗多种疾病，包括免疫缺陷、遗传性失明、血友病以及最近的亨廷顿病（一种致命的神经系统疾病）。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/noninvasive-monitoring-of-gene-expression-in-primate-brains2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 10:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/noninvasive-monitoring-of-gene-expression-in-primate-brains</guid></item><item><title>造血干细胞移植</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/hematopoietic-stem-cell-transplantation</link><description>造血干细胞移植（HPSCT）有时也称为骨髓移植，涉及向骨髓功能障碍或耗尽的患者施用健康的造血干细胞。临床使用的HPSCT有多种类型，移植细胞可以从多种来源获得。该手术有几个好处，可用于治疗恶性和非恶性疾病。它有助于增强骨髓功能。此外，根据所治疗的疾病，它可能会破坏恶性肿瘤细胞。它还可以产生功能细胞，在免疫缺陷综合症、血红蛋白病和其他疾病等情况下取代功能失调的细胞。 HPSCT 后的存活率正在增加，但手术并发症导致的发病率仍在继续。本活动回顾了 HPSCT 的适应症、获取供体细胞的不同选择，包括每种选择的优点和缺点，以及该过程的急性和慢性并发症。此外，它还强调了跨专业团队在管理接受 HPSCT 的患者方面的作用，以改善患者的治疗结果并减少与手术相关的发病率。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hematopoietic-stem-cell-transplantation.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 10:40:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/hematopoietic-stem-cell-transplantation</guid></item><item><title>小鼠研究实现了突破性的 100% 寿命延长</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/breakthrough-100-life-extension-achieved-in-mouse-study</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 10:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/breakthrough-100-life-extension-achieved-in-mouse-study</guid></item><item><title>全身炎症标志物与脑小血管疾病进展的关联基于社区的前瞻性研究</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/association-of-systemic-inflammatory-markers-with-cerebral-small-vessel-disease-progressiona-community-based-prospective-study</link><description>本研究调查了中性粒细胞与淋巴细胞比率、单核细胞与淋巴细胞比率以及全身免疫炎症指数与 CSVD 进展之间的关系。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/association-of-systemic-inflammatory-markers-with-cerebral-small-vessel-disease-progressiona-community-based-prospective-study2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 10:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/association-of-systemic-inflammatory-markers-with-cerebral-small-vessel-disease-progressiona-community-based-prospective-study</guid></item></channel></rss>